{
  "id": "adv_bond_smr_01_02",
  "title": "奥山すみれ2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "（あれ……kanaさんが一人でけん玉をしてる！）\n（レッスン着まで着て真剣な表情……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Oh… kana-san is playing Kendama by herself!）\n（Wearing a lesson uniform and with a serious expression…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 1.7666667581,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "（……もしかしてkanaさんもけん玉が好きなのかな？）\n（声を掛けてみようっと！）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…Maybe kana-san likes Kendama‚ too?）\n（Let's talk!）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 10.3333334248,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 7666.666575200001
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "kanaさー……ん……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "kana-sanー…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan001.m4a",
      "text": "あーーーっ！　なんでkanaがけん玉なんて\n練習しなきゃいけないわけ！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahーーー! Why does kana\nhave to practice Kendama!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 20.7999999644,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan002.m4a",
      "text": "一週間でけん玉マスターしろなんて無理に\n決まってんじゃん！　やるけどさぁ！　やるけど！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mastering Kendama in a week is obviously\nimpossible! But‚ I'll do it! I'll do it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.6333332977,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan003.m4a",
      "text": "くっそ……こんな赤い玉についた小さな穴に\nこの棒が刺さるかっての！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Damn… how can this stick even fit through\nthat tiny hole in this red ball!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.1999989471,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan004.m4a",
      "text": "ムカつく……マージでイライラしてきた……\nドリルでこの穴広げてやろうかな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So triggering… really starting to get annoying…\nShould I drill this hole…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 41.0333322805,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan005.m4a",
      "text": "ん？　すみれじゃん。何見てんの？\nスタジオはkanaが予約してたんだけどー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Umm? Sumire-chan. What are you looking at?\nkana had booked the studioー",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.7999971669,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr004.m4a",
      "text": "えっと……kanaさんがけん玉してたので……\n好きなのかなって……私もけん玉好きなので……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well… kana-san was playing Kendama…\nI wonder if you like it… I like Kendama‚ too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 57.1333292286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan006.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ？　これ見てkanaがけん玉好きに見える？\nどう見たってやらされてる感半端ないっしょ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hah? Does this make you think kana likes Kendama?\nNo matter where you look‚ it's all forced",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7333282113,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr005.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあどうしてけん玉を……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ why Kendama…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1333317717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan007.m4a",
      "text": "はあ……。『けん玉戦士ケンケンパッ！』？　っていう\nアニメのPRをすることになって――",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa…. I ended up promoting an anime――\ncalled \"Kendama Warrior Ken-ken-pat\"?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.2000025074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr006.m4a",
      "text": "わぁっ、凄いっ！　それ、けん玉界隈で話題になってる\nアニメです！　ちびっこ人気も高いんですよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ that's amazing! That anime is a hot issue in the\nKendama industry! It's also popular with children!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 86.1666768034,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr007.m4a",
      "text": "コミカライズや劇場版も決まりましたし\nこれからもっともっと有名になると思います！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It has also been decided that it will be made into a comic book and a movie\nI think it will become more and more famous in the future!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.4666752776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan008.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうなの……？\nてか、このアニメそんなに凄かったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-Is that so…?\nWell‚ is this anime that great?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 99.5333419443,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr008.m4a",
      "text": "はい！　とっても凄いです！\nいいなぁ～、私もけん玉のお仕事してみたいです～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! It's really amazing!\nThat's cool~‚ I'd love to work with Kendama‚ too~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.500008611,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan009.m4a",
      "text": "（kanaはけん玉詳しくないし、この仕事……）\n（一人でやるより、すみれも一緒の方が都合がいいかも？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（kana doesn't know much about Kendama‚ so this…）\n（Rather than doing it alone‚ it might be more convenient to do it with Sumire?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.3666742604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan010.m4a",
      "text": "……ねえ、すみれちゃん。{user}には\nkanaから話つけとくから一緒にこの仕事やらない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey‚ Sumire-chan. kana will talk to\n{user}‚ do you want to do this together?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 124.5000070851,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr009.m4a",
      "text": "え……？　ええええええっ！？！？！\nいいいいいい、いいんですか！？！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh…? Ehhhhhh!?!?!\nI-I-I-I-I-I-Is it okay!?!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.5333363494,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kan",
      "speakerName": "kana",
      "speakerNameEn": "kana",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kana.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-kan011.m4a",
      "text": "うんっ！　そのかわり、kanaにけん玉教えてよ\nそれから、絶対にkanaより目立たないこと、いい？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah! Instead‚ teach kana how to play Kendama\nAnd‚ never stand out more than kana‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 136.6666696828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sumire",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02/sud_vo_adv_bond_smr_01_02-smr010.m4a",
      "text": "はいっ！　もちろんです！　任せて下さい！\nkanaさんをけん玉マスターにしちゃいますっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yes! Of course! Leave it to me!\nI'll make kana-san a Kendama master!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 146.4666605275,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}